title: House and land price index in Canada 2018
summary: The graph shows the House land Index development in House 2018 .
The starting point was just shy of 1005 dollars in January but skyrocketed to over 1030 dollars in May .
A continouus , but a lot less steeper incline happend in between May and December , finishing at around 1033.0 dollars in December .
gold: The graph shows the house and land price index in canada in the year of 2018 . It is striking that the value only changes twice a year . It falls from January to February , and from May to July it rises back to the original amount of 1033 .
